comments.body:
You might want to export these interfaces so that they are reachable, i.e.:

```ts
import { v1, V1Options } from "uuid";

const options: V1Options = {
  clockseq: 0,
  msecs: Date.now()
};

v1(options);
```

Otherwise anyone using the types would have to repeat the definitions themselves since they're not exported.

